# test_types
: Test table covering all column types
- id int *pk
- age tinyint
: TinyInt for small integers (0-255)
- quantity smallint
: SmallInt for medium integers
- population bigint
: BigInt for very large integers
- note tinytext
: TinyText for short text
- price decimal10,2
: Decimal with precision and scale
- description mediumtext
: MediumText for longer content
- content longtext
: LongText for very long content
- code char10
: Char fixed length string
- birth_year year
: Year column for years
- created_at datetime
: DateTime for timestamps without timezone
